```bash
mcp__hex-ssh__remote-ssh:
  "curl -fsS -X POST http://127.0.0.1:${VPS_RELAY_HOOK_PORT}/memory/add -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{\"category\":\"operator_pref\",\"text\":\"<text>\"}'"
```

Forget: `POST /memory/forget {"memory_id":N}` or `{"tag_match":"..."}`.

